<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="firm-adj">firm <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fɜːm/    美 /fɜːrm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>坚硬的；牢固的；稳固的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The city walls are as firm as rock. 
城墙坚如磐石。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Make sure the ladder feels firm before you climb up.
爬梯子前要确保它的稳固。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>坚定的；坚决的；强有力的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is firm in his purpose. 
他意志坚定。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Go ahead for a firm goal, and the whole world will let you go!
向着坚定的目标前进，整个世界都会为你让路！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Have a firm handshake.
握手要坚实有力。</p><footer>2008 安徽</footer></div></div>